run for your wife is a uk-made 2012 film , based on the theatre farce run for your wife , written by ray cooney , who along with john luton also directed the film . upon release the film was savaged by critics and has been referred to as one of the worst films of all time , after it grossed just £ 602 in its opening weekend at the british box office to its £ 900,000 budget . it was released on 14 february 2013 .